text: The Iceland women's national under-16 basketball team is a national basketball team of Iceland, administered by the Icelandic Basketball Federation.Profile - Iceland, FIBA.basketball It represents the country in women's international under-16 basketball competitions. The team won three gold and one silver medals at the FIBA U16 Women's European Championship Division C. ==See also== *Iceland women's national basketball team *Iceland women's national under-18 basketball team *Iceland men's national under-16 basketball team ==References== ==External links== *Archived records of Iceland team participations Category:Basketball in Iceland Category:Women's national under-16 basketball teams Category:Women's national sports teams of Iceland
